item.title: LKGK-12-fully-enclosed-inflatable-cabinet
item.description: LCGK-12 fully insulated and fully enclosed inflatable metal switchgear referred to as inflatable cabinet is also known as common box type inflatable cabinet, sf6 inflatable cabinet. All its live parts are completely sealed in a 3.0mm thick stainless steel SF6 gas box, multiple branch switches can be installed in one gas box, so that the switchgear is not affected by the environment. It truly realizes functions such as maintenance-free, reliable operation, and unattended operation. The inflatable cabinet unit adopts a modular design, which can be flexibly expanded and scientifically combined.
